Panier des Sens Lime Blossom Linen Water, 33.8 fl. oz.
Lime Blossom is a beautiful green and light floral aroma, like a soft breeze of spring. Linen water will leave a gentle, light and fresh scent and is a subtle way to add fragrance to the home to give that "oh-so French" touch and smell.
